1. *Pad* je bio neizbežan nakon što su igrači ostali bez snage. (Fall was inevitable after the players ran out of energy.)
2. Lopta je *pala* na zemlju nakon što ju je igrač odbio. (The ball fell to the ground after the player hit it back.)
3. Planinari su se opremili sa *padobranima* pre nego što su skočili iz aviona. (The mountaineers equipped themselves with parachutes before jumping out of the plane.)
4. Njen *pad* u depresiju je bio nagao i nepredvidiv. (Her fall into depression was sudden and unpredictable.)
5. Proizvođači telefona uvode nove modele svake godine kako bi sprečili *pad* prodaje. (Phone manufacturers introduce new models every year to prevent a drop in sales.)
6. Ova godina beleži *pad* turizma zbog pandemije koronavirusa. (This year marks a decline in tourism due to the coronavirus pandemic.)
7. *Padanje* snega je izazvalo gužve na putevima. (The falling snow caused traffic jams.)
8. Košarkaš je učinio spektakularan *pad* dok je pokušavao da uhvati loptu. (The basketball player made a spectacular fall while trying to catch the ball.)
9. Ispitivači su testirali *otpornost na pad* ovog mobilnog telefona. (Testers have tested this mobile phone's drop resistance.)
10. *Padobran* se otvorio u poslednji čas i spasio život padobrancu. (The parachute opened just in time and saved the skydiver's life.)